(243, 'Vibigaba Turmeric Germ Rice Box 1Kg', '4.00', 'Vibigaba Turmeric Germ rice is rice that has its embryos intact for germination under the right conditions so that the enzymes in the rice grain are activated to create many nutrients, especially the natural content of Gaba (gamma aminobutyric acid) is 6 10 times higher. compared with brown rice. Rice also adds fresh turmeric essence to help promote health protection from sprouted rice.\r\nRice is grown in a concentrated raw material area, processed according to the European HACCP process, surpassing 603 strict Japanese criteria, ensuring a clear origin, quality commitment to consumers.\r\nEffects of Vibigaba Turmeric germ rice:\r\n\r\nHelps reduce stomach and duodenal ulcers', 3, 'img239.png', 100),
(244, 'ST24 Organic Broken Rice 1Kg', '2.00', 'HOA MILK ORGANIC RICE - HIGH QUALITY VIETNAM PRODUCTS\r\n\r\n- 100% organic ST24 rice.\r\n\r\n- Non-GMO (Non GMO), cultivated and processed according to American and European organic standards.\r\n\r\nCharacteristics of rice: Fragrant, soft, medium-sweet rice\r\n\r\nCooking method: to keep the delicate taste of rice, cook with less water. Should only be submerged 1cm, no need to stir. The rice grains are cooked evenly and are spongy.\r\n\r\nST24 rice specialties have been voted as delicious rice, specifically:\r\n\r\n- Won the first prize of Delicious Rice Contest 2017\r\n\r\n- Won Top 3 \"World\'s Delicious Rice 2017\" at MACAU', 3, 'img240.png', 100),
(245, 'Traditional Organic White Rice OrgaRice 1Kg', '2.00', 'OrgaRICE organic rice is grown according to the square model of natural shrimp, 6 months of rice cultivation, 6 months of shrimp farming. From the one-year, one-crop season rice variety in the natural rice-shrimp farming area of Thanh Phu district, Ben Tre province, the rich alluvial land is famous for the \"Shrimp-Rice\" model. The \"Shrimp-Rice\" model is a model of growing 1 rice crop intercropped with 1 shrimp crop, taking advantage of the time when salt water does not penetrate, absolutely do not use pesticides so as not to affect the shrimp crop. . Therefore, rice grains are fragrant, delicious, and softer than ordinary rice, ensuring clean and safe for users. 100% organic rice certified organic by the European Union EU and the US Department of Agriculture USDA', 3, 'img241.png', 100),
(246, 'Orgarice Organic White Rice 1Kg', '2.00', 'Organic white rice is grown under strict organic process, complying with international standards EU - Europe USDA - USA AS - Japan No use of chemical fertilizers, pesticides, herbicides Only Use regulated organic fertilizers. The place where rice is grown is the intersection of the lower Mekong River and the East Sea, with a specific climate, so each grain of rice is imbued with sweet taste, natural fragrance with many essential minerals. Organic milled white rice is produced from ST24 rice variety, meets the standards of long grain, clear white, medium pliable and smells of pandan leaves; reached the top 3 best rice in the world at the International Rice Trade Conference 2017.', 3, 'img242.png', 100),
(247, 'PB Farm Organic Rice Vinegar 200ml', '3.00', 'PB Farm Organic Rice Vinegar 200ml\r\nOrigin: Thailand\r\nCertified organic USDA, EU\r\nIngredients: 100% organic jasmine brown rice vinegar\r\n\r\nRice vinegar is a fermented product from rice, with its abundance of nutrients and low acidity, it is an integral part of a healthy diet. However, not only used in cooking, rice vinegar also has many health benefits such as boosting immunity, regulating blood pressure, preventing infections and detoxifying the body.\r\n\r\n1. Skin care\r\nThis vinegar can be applied directly to the skin, especially when mixed with tea tree oil. It can act as an astringent to tighten skin and prevent certain infections, while soothing inflammation and improving your skin\'s radiance.\r\n\r\n2. Improves Immune System\r\nThis vinegar is rich in amino acids that are important for your immune system function, reducing the activity of free radicals in the body.\r\n\r\n3. Prevents Heart Problems\r\nResearch has shown that rice vinegar can slow the deposition of cholesterol in the arteries and blood vessels, helping you avoid heart diseases like atherosclerosis, heart attacks and strokes.\r\n\r\n4. Promotes Digestion\r\nCertain active ingredients, such as acetic acid, present in rice vinegar have the ability to calm inflammation in the intestines, while promoting peristalsis and normal bowel movements.\r\n\r\n5. Liver tonic\r\nFor centuries, rice vinegar has been popularly used in Japan as a liver tonic. It is thought to increase the detoxifying effects of this organ and ensure that it functions properly.\r\n\r\n6. Increase energy level\r\nThere are key amino acids and other active ingredients in rice vinegar that can help your body fight fatigue and boost your metabolism exactly when you need it. Using this vinegar as a salad dressing during your day can help fuel you up for the afternoon activity.', 3, 'img243.png', 100),
(248, 'Bragg Organic Apple Cider Vinegar', '8.00', 'Bragg brand organic apple cider vinegar is the most trusted apple cider vinegar in the US as well as worldwide with ingredients from natural apples and certified organic by USDA.\r\nMedicinal uses\r\n\r\nPrevention of diabetes\r\nWeight loss\r\nLowering Cholesteron\r\nPurify the body, detox\r\nSinus clearance\r\nCure sore throat\r\nDigestive support\r\nRelieve pain from sunburn or insect bites\r\nCooking Uses: Organic Apple Cider Vinegar for salad dressing, beauty...\r\n\r\nBeauty Uses\r\n\r\nWhiten, smooth skin.\r\nShrink pores.\r\nReduces oiliness on the skin.\r\nAcne treatment\r\nLotion\r\nRestore sunburned skin\r\nTo get rid of dandruff....', 3, 'img244.png', 100),
(249, 'Shelled Organic Pumpkin Seeds Sottolestelle 200g', '6.00', 'Organic Peeled Pumpkin Seeds Sottolestelle 200g\r\nContains high levels of phytosterols, L-tryptophan compounds\r\n Rich in zinc, Vitamin E and B vitamins.\r\nReduces bad cholesterol levels: Pumpkin seeds are high in phytosterols\r\nThis is an antioxidant that works to eliminate bad cholesterol in the body.\r\n \r\nIngredients: 100% peeled organic pumpkin seeds\r\n \r\nUser manual:\r\nCan be used as a nutritious nut milk, eaten immediately or mixed with snacks, yogurt, cereals, and smoothies. Or can also be chopped and mixed with other dishes.\r\nRecommended audience\r\n1. Pregnant mothers\r\n2. People with digestive problems\r\n3. People with diabetes, cancer\r\n4. People with cardiovascular diseases\r\n5. People with high pressure at work, reduce stress Storage: store in a refrigerator\r\n \r\nOrigin: Sottolestelle – Italy\r\nShelf Life: 24 months from date of manufacture', 3, 'img245.png', 100),
(250, 'Markal Organic Pumpkin Seeds 500g', '12.00', 'INGREDIENTS 100% organic pumpkin seeds Net weight: 500g\r\nUSES\r\n- Reduce bad cholesterol levels\r\n- Help you sleep well\r\n- Anti-osteoporosis\r\n- Prevents the aging process\r\n- Generate energy and support blood cell production\r\n- Anti-inflammatory, good for digestion\r\nHOW TO USE Use directly or combine with other dishes and drinks\r\nHOW TO STORAGE Store in a cool, dry place, away from direct sunlight', 3, 'img246.png', 100),
(251, 'Amavie Foods Organic Chia Seeds 500g', '9.00', 'Ingredients: 100% Organic Black Chia Seeds\r\nOrigin: Peru\r\nDirections for use: Add chia seeds to nut milk, fruit juice, and others at a ratio of 1:4. When the seeds bloom evenly, depending on preference, you can use them directly or add nuts, fruits, cereals...\r\nStorage: Seal the bag for better preservation. Store in a place protected from sunlight and dry.', 3, 'img247.png', 100),
(252, 'Organic Wheat Grass Seeds Sotto 500g', '5.00', 'From wheat seeds you can grow wheatgrass or collect wheat germ from sprouting wheatgrass seeds.\r\nWheat germ provides more protein than most meats we use on a daily basis, and contains 23 other nutrients, including potassium, calcium, zinc and magnesium. Vitamins E, A, B-1 and B-3 are present in high concentrations; They help the body maintain heart and lung condition and maintain high energy levels.\r\nWheatgrass contains about 13 vitamins, 10 minerals, 17 amino acids and more than a hundred enzymes beneficial to human health.\r\nWheatgrass is considered an excellent supplement in the process of weight loss, very rich in nutrients, low in calories and fat-free.\r\nThey are high in fiber, low in calories, and packed with vitamins and minerals. They are an especially good source of manganese, selenium, phosphorus and magnesium.\r\nTo get the best value from Wheat Grass. You should choose wheat grass seeds with organic certification such as EU, USDA...', 3, 'img248.png', 100),
(253, 'Lotus Seeds Mixed 3 Colors - 500g', '10.00', 'Mixed quinoa contains 3 colors: white, black, red. This seed contains many minerals, magnesium, vitamins A, E, D, F, phosphorus, rich in vitamin E and Omega 3 fatty acids, Omage 6... very good for health.\r\n \r\nCooking method: Wash with water, drain. Cooking quinoa is basically the same way as rice. Can be cooked on the stovetop, in the microwave or in the rice cooker.\r\n \r\nUsing:\r\nQuinoa can be used in combination with the following dishes:\r\n- Use to mix salads\r\n- Cook with rice, soup, porridge\r\n- Make baby food with fruit\r\nWeight: 500g\r\nImported directly from Australia\r\nHSD: 12 months from date of manufacture', 3, 'img249.png', 100),
(254, 'Organic Tri-Color Mixed Quinoa Seeds Sottolestelle 250g', '6.00', 'Quinoa contains about 15% protein, contains all the essential amino acids (the body cannot synthesize) found in cereals and milk such as Lysine is an amino acid for muscle growth and regeneration. (substrate to create collagen, a protective film of the skin that is always smooth, soft and youthful). Amino acids in quinoa are more balanced than in grains, millet, etc. In quinoa contains many good proteins for the body, but it is gluten-free, an amino acid that causes indigestion in the elderly, children and people with gluten intolerance (the amino acid mainly found in grains).\r\nIngredients: Quinoa blends include three types of quinoa: white, black, and red.\r\n \r\nInstructions for use: Wash the quinoa seeds, cook for 10 minutes on low heat with twice as much water as quinoa. Then turn off the heat, cover and let the quinoa seeds expand and absorb the water gradually. Can be used as a salad, eaten hot or cold, cooked with soup, milk, fried with other vegetables...\r\n*Preserved in dry, cool place. Avoid sources of high heat and humidity. Better stored in glass jars. Seal tightly after each use.\r\nOrigin: Sottolestelle – Italy\r\nShelf Life: 24 months from date of manufacture\r\nEuropean organic certification\r\nVegan\r\nNon-GMO', 3, 'img250.png', 100),
(255, 'Organic White Quinoa Sottolestelle-500Gr', '9.00', 'Certified Organic Europe Certified Organic Italy Vegan Non GMO Gluten Free Rich in protein, fiber, amino acids, lysine, Quinoa contains a lot of Riboflavin (B2) which is a B vitamin Suitable for vegetarians and vegans nutrition, eat clean, in weight loss diet\r\nProvide essential protein (especially vegetarians)\r\n\r\nQuinoa contains about 15% protein, contains all the essential amino acids (the body cannot synthesize) found in cereals and milk such as Lysine is an amino acid for muscle growth and regeneration. (substrate to create collagen, a protective film of the skin that is always smooth, soft and youthful). Amino acids in quinoa are more balanced than in grains, millet, etc.\r\n\r\nIn quinoa contains many good proteins for the body, but it is gluten-free, an amino acid that causes indigestion in the elderly, children and people with gluten intolerance (the amino acid mainly found in grains).\r\n\r\nQuinoa has twice the fiber content of whole grains. The fiber in quinoa is mainly beta-glucan soluble fiber, so it helps stabilize blood sugar much more effectively than regular grains. Especially good for people with type 2 diabetes.\r\n\r\nQuinoa contains an extremely complex starch called a complex carbohydrate with a low glycemic index \"low glycemic index\", so when eaten it will make us feel full but not provide as much carbohydrate as grains and white rice we eat every day.\r\n\r\nQuinoa contains all the essential amino acids, so it is very good for pregnant women as well as children at the developmental stage. Because essential amino acids are essential to the process of forming and perfecting organs in the fetus as well as in young children.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nIn addition, quinoa contains many minerals such as calcium, phosphorus, copper, zinc, especially iron. Because pregnant women need 2-3 times more iron than normal people to form red blood cells of the fetus, helping the fetus to develop normally in the future. Iron helps to increase concentration in young children.\r\n\r\nQuinoa seeds contain a lot of Riboflavin (B2), a B vitamin, this vitamin helps to increase absorption, regenerate energy and increase oxygen to the brain and muscles to help reduce headaches effectively.\r\n\r\nIn addition, quinoa also contains many antioxidants that help the body increase resistance.\r\n\r\nIn addition, quinoa seeds have countless other uses such as: enhancing memory, fighting osteoporosis in the elderly (pre- and postmenopausal women), making teeth stronger, fighting anemia, anti-inflammatory, etc. prevent cancer…\r\n\r\nAUDIENCE USED:\r\n\r\nWomen preparing and getting pregnant\r\nBreastfeeding mothers and babies eating solid foods\r\nVegetarians and athletes\r\nPeople with diabetes and heart disease\r\nStroke, high blood cholesterol\r\nWomen in menopause\r\nPeople who want to lose weight and beautify their skin\r\nPeople who want to improve their health\r\nPeople who want to supplement with adequate nutrition but do not want to be fat…\r\nWash the quinoa and cook for 10 minutes on low heat with twice the amount of water as the quino. Then turn off the heat, cover and let the quinoa seeds expand and absorb the water gradually. Can be used as a salad, eaten hot or cold, cooked with soup, milk, sautéed with other vegetables', 3, 'img251.png', 100),
(256, 'Organic Cashew Nuts Organic 500g', '12.00', 'Cashew nuts after separating the hard shell will still have a silk shell, this silk shell not only protects the cashew kernel inside, but also creates a beautiful shape for the cashew nut. After being salted, the blend of this silk skin with salt, combined with the fleshy taste of cashew kernels, when eaten, will be very fragrant, crispy, light salty, bar.\r\nThe product is USDA certified organic.', 3, 'img252.png', 100),
