(320, 'Organic Italian Grape Sugar Sottolestelle 250ml', '10.00', 'Organic Grape Sugar 250ml Sottolestelle Organic Grape Sugar\r\n\r\nSweetener with a consistency similar to honey obtained by concentrating organic grape juice. Due to its composition, it has superior sweetening power compared to traditional sugar, so with the same recipe it can be used in less quantity than sugar. Suitable for sweetening all food products, without changing their taste.\r\nGrape sugar is a natural sweetener used for baby food and drinks.\r\nCavity free, gluten free. Completely 100% organic. No GMOs.\r\nSugar is easily dissolved in baby foods and drinks such as orange juice, lemonade, and smoothies. Mom can prepare tea and cakes in the easiest way.\r\nSugar does not cause obesity, convenient for diabetics.\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% organic grape sugar concentrate\r\nUser manual:\r\n– Mixing fruit juice and cooking tea are both delicious???\r\n- Store in a cool, dry place.\r\nCover tightly after use, and store at refrigerator temperature after opening.\r\n\r\nOrigin: Sottolestelle – Italy\r\nShelf Life: 24 months from date of manufacture\r\nEuropean organic certification\r\nVegan\r\nNon-GMO', 3, 'img316.png', 100),
