(391, 'Vinasamex Organic Anise Powder 40g', '4.00', 'Ingredients: 100% Vietnamese organic anise powder\r\nMade in Viet Nam\r\nInstructions for use: Use as a cooking seasoning\r\nStorage: Store in a cool, dry place, away from direct sunlight\r\nCertified organic EU, USDA, JAS, Korea\r\n\r\nWith the motto of accompanying upland farmers, VINASAMEX brings long-term cooperation for mutual development, dedicated to taking care of the interests and prosperous life of farmers. From 2017 to now, with an effort to improve knowledge of sustainable agriculture for the highlanders, VINASAMEX continuously expands the production model of cinnamon, anise and organic spices. From 868 hectares of organic cinnamon and anise, associated with 418 households in 2017, so far, VINASAMEX has built 4367 hectares of organic cinnamon, anise and turmeric material areas, associated with 2115 households in Yen provinces. Bai, Lang Son, Lao Cai and Bac Can. People associated with VINASAMEX are able to consume 100% of their output at a price higher than the market price, guaranteed income, peace of mind in production, and improved living standards.', 6, 'img387.png', 100),
(392, 'Organic Lemon Leaves Powder Lumlum30g', '4.00', 'Kaffir is a type of lemon with a characteristic aroma originating from Thailand. Thai lime leaves are thick, glossy and dark green leaves, an indispensable spice in Southeast Asian cuisine. Thai lime leaf powder helps to add a unique flavor to stir-fries, curries, salads,\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% Thai Lemon Leaves\r\n\r\nHow to use\r\n\r\nLemon leaf powder helps dishes to increase flavor and aroma. They can create a balance for spicy dishes, in addition, lime leaf powder also brings a stronger, richer flavor to the dish. But if using too much lime leaf powder will make the dish bitter, you should be careful when using it. Just 1/3 teaspoon of lime leaf powder will have the same flavor as 1 dried lemon leaf.\r\nNot only used in food, but lemon leaf powder is also used in drinks such as soda, cocktails and very popular vodka flavor.\r\nIn addition to being used as a spice for dishes, making dishes more delicious, lemon leaf powder also has many good health benefits. Lemon leaves help treat coughs, respiratory diseases, colds, asthma, aid digestion.', 6, 'img388.png', 100),
(393, 'Organic Seasoning Powder for Baby Miles DM Bio290g', '7.00', 'Extracted from the natural sweetness of vegetables, spices and organic herbs, 100% natural.\r\n✔️ The seasoning is soft, smooth, like soup powder, sweet from vegetables, suitable as a seasoning for children, making soups, porridge, soups, stews, baking, stir-frying...\r\n✔️ Create rich taste, natural sweetness for dishes, supplement vitamins and minerals to help promote health and prevent disease.\r\n✔️ Good for the digestive system, no side effects, safe for children, pregnant women and the elderly.\r\n✔️ Help children who are hungry to eat more\r\n✔️ Suitable for vegetarians.\r\n✔️ Does not contain cholesterol (suitable for people with high blood pressure, fatty blood ...)\r\n✔️ No preservatives, colorants and flavors.', 6, 'img389.png', 100),
(394, 'Organic Vegetable Seasoning Powder Sottolestelle100g', '4.00', 'Seasoning powder in the form of easy-to-dissolve tablets, helps shorten the time of stewing vegetables and fruits as usual while still giving the broth natural color and natural aroma like a well-cooked stew.\r\n\r\nVegetable seasoning powder with Sottolestelle\'s drying technology and unique processing secret helps preserve fiber and minerals in each ingredient, not only safe and natural, but also helps your family\'s meals more peaceful, full of flavor.\r\n\r\nSalient features of Sottolestelle Organic Vegetable Seasoning Powder:\r\n\r\n- No MSG, No Additives\r\n\r\n- No added preservatives and artificial colors\r\n\r\n- The ingredients are completely natural\r\n\r\nOrganic seasoning powder is suitable for vegetarians, dieters, eatclean, macrobiotics, etc., especially suitable for babies in the weaning period.', 6, 'img390.png', 100),
(395, 'Dace Organic Turmeric Powder40g', '3.00', 'Certification: Certified organic according to USDA standards of the US, EU standards of Europe and JAS standards of Japan.\r\nOrigin: Product is made in Vietnam\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% Dried Organic Turmeric.\r\n\r\nNet weight: 55g.\r\n\r\nExpiry date: Printed on the package.\r\n\r\nSuggested use: Use to marinate ingredients, color dishes, season dishes.\r\n\r\nStorage Instructions: Store in a cool, dry place. Keep out of reach of CHILDREN.\r\n\r\nOrigin – Certification: The product is manufactured in Vietnam and certified organic according to USDA standards of the US, EU standards of Europe and JAS standards of Japan.', 6, 'img391.png', 100),
(396, 'Organic Turmeric Powder Lumlum30g', '4.00', 'Turmeric powder contains high active ingredient Curcumin, which helps to increase anti-inflammatory, antioxidant and anti-bacterial effect.\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% organic turmeric\r\n\r\nUses\r\n\r\nTurmeric powder has the effect of supporting the treatment of many diseases and protecting human health. It helps prevent and cure diseases of the stomach, duodenum, liver and diseases of the immune system such as arthritis, systemic inflammation .... Turmeric starch also helps to eliminate, destroy blood stasis, remove toxins in the human body.\r\n\r\nHow to use\r\n\r\nTurmeric is a commonly used spice in cooking, as an ingredient in curries, a spice commonly used in Asian and Indian cuisines.\r\n\r\nIn addition, turmeric is also a familiar ingredient with healing and beauty effects.', 6, 'img392.png', 100),
