(398, 'Dace Organic Chili Powder 45g', '4.00', 'Certification: Certified organic according to USDA standards of the US, EU standards of Europe and JAS standards of Japan.\r\n\r\nOrigin: Product is made in Vietnam\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% Dried Organic Chili.\r\n\r\nNet weight: 45g.\r\n\r\nExpiry date: Printed on the package.\r\n\r\nSuggested use: Use to marinate ingredients, make dipping sauces, season dishes.\r\n\r\nStorage Instructions: Store in a cool, dry place. Keep out of reach of CHILDREN', 6, 'img394.png', 100),
(399, 'Organic Chili Powder Lumlum30g', '4.00', 'Chili is a pungent and warm spice, often used in Asian Cuisine, to stimulate the taste buds and bring out a distinctive flavor to the dish.\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% organic chili\r\n\r\nUses: Chili also works very well for weight loss, helps prevent aging, and keeps the body young for a long time. In chili powder contains many nutrients, vitamins A, C, and potassium, which regulate the body\'s physiological functions, aid digestion, and burn excess fat.\r\n\r\nUsage: Used in marinating and processing grilled, hot pot, fried, squishy, ... is an indispensable condiment in kimchi, Tom Yum\r\n\r\nPreserved in dry, cool place. Close the lid tightly after each use', 6, 'img395.png', 100),
(400, 'Vinasamex Organic Chilli Powder 40g', '3.00', 'Vietnam Cinnamon Export and Production Joint Stock Company (VINASAMEX., JSC) was established in 2012, on the basis of nearly 10 years of experience in the field of production and sales of cinnamon, anise and cinnamon products. spice. VINASAMEX is a pioneering premium star anise brand in Vietnam that builds and manufactures under a closed value chain to produce pure quality products from the Northern mountains and forests, sustainably accompanying highland farmers, representative to raise the level of Vietnamese anise cinnamon products in the international market.\r\n\r\nWith the motto of accompanying upland farmers, VINASAMEX brings long-term cooperation for mutual development, dedicated to taking care of the interests and prosperous life of farmers. From 2017 to now, with an effort to improve knowledge of sustainable agriculture for the highlanders, VINASAMEX continuously expands the production model of cinnamon, anise and organic spices. From 868 hectares of organic cinnamon and anise, associated with 418 households in 2017, so far, VINASAMEX has built 4367 hectares of organic cinnamon, anise and turmeric material areas, associated with 2115 households in Yen provinces. Bai, Lang Son, Lao Cai and Bac Can. People associated with VINASAMEX are able to consume 100% of their output at a price higher than the market price, guaranteed income, peace of mind in production, and improved living standards.', 6, 'img396.png', 100),
(401, 'Farmers Organic Cinnamon Powder40g', '2.00', 'Origin: Vietnam Certified organic USDA, EU\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% organic cinnamon ingredients\r\nPRODUCT USE - Cinnamon contains many vitamins and minerals such as calcium, iron, manganese, zinc, magnesium, vitamin A, niacin..., in addition, it is also rich in fiber and antioxidants so it is used as a flavoring agent. precious medicine in oriental medicine. In cuisine, cinnamon is used a lot for sweet and savory dishes. They help effectively eliminate fishy odors on fish and meat while creating an attractive flavor for each dish. – Put a small amount of cinnamon in soups, chicken porridge srx to help children prevent diarrhea and fight bacteria. Cinnamon is not only used in Vietnam, they are also very famous and appear in many Japanese and American favorite dishes.\r\nSPECIAL CHARACTERISTICS\r\nCinnamon is not only a precious medicinal herb but also a very special spice.\r\n– With the material area in Yen Bai, Ho Tieu Viet has selected the best type of cinnamon as input materials.\r\n– The minimum essential oil level is 4%, Cinnamon Vipep not only has the most typical sweet aroma of Cinnamon but also very beautiful.\r\n– Cinnamon Vipep is the only product on the market that is sterilized with modern lines.\r\n– Products are exported to the following markets: USA and Canada.', 6, 'img397.png', 100),
(402, 'Vinasamex Organic Cinnamon Powder 40g', '4.00', 'Made in Viet Nam\r\nCertified organic USDA, EU, Japan\r\nIngredients: 100% organic cinnamon stick\r\n\r\nCinnamon is a very tasty spice. It has been prized for its medicinal properties for thousands of years.\r\n\r\nCinnamon is high in cinnamaldehyde, which is believed to be responsible for most of cinnamon\'s health benefits. The health benefits of this spice include:\r\n\r\nHigh levels of polyphenol antioxidants help protect your body from damage caused by free radicals. Even its effects go beyond garlic and oregano. It can be used as a natural preservative for products\r\n\r\nCinnamon\'s powerful anti-inflammatory properties help the body fight infections and repair tissue damage\r\n\r\nCinnamon may improve several key risk factors for heart disease, including cholesterol, triglycerides, and blood pressure. The regular use of 120mg of cinnamon per day has an effective effect on the above conditions\r\n\r\nCinnamon has been shown to significantly increase insulin sensitivity. By increasing insulin sensitivity, cinnamon can lower blood sugar\r\n\r\nCinnamon has been shown to lower fasting blood sugar, having a strong anti-diabetic effect when taken 1-6g or 0.5-2 teaspoons daily.\r\n\r\nAnimal and test-tube studies indicate that cinnamon may have protective effects against cancer.\r\n\r\nCinnamaldehyde, the main active ingredient in cinnamon, has antifungal and antibacterial properties that can reduce infections and help fight tooth decay and bad breath.\r\n\r\nTest-tube studies have shown that cinnamon may help fight HIV-1, the main human HIV virus. HIV is a virus that slows down your immune system, which can eventually lead to AIDS, if left untreated. Cinnamon extracted from Cassia varieties is said to help fight HIV-1, the most common strain of HIV virus in humans\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nUsage: Used in cooking, drinks...', 6, 'img398.png', 100),
(403, 'Cinnamon Powder Vipep35g', '1.00', 'Cinnamon is a plant quite familiar to life, can be used as both a spice and a medicine from time immemorial.\r\nCinnamon powder has a very fragrant smell and keeps the scent for a long time. Cinnamon powder contains a lot of vitamins and minerals such as: Vitamin A, niacin, pantothenic acid, pyridoxine, calcium, potassium, manganese, iron, zinc and magnesium. In addition, it contains a large amount of fiber and antioxidants. It is estimated that 1 tablespoon of cinnamon powder contains up to 1.4 mg of manganese, equivalent to nearly 75% of the body\'s recommended daily amount of manganese.\r\nCinnamon Powder Vipep Jar 35g\r\nCinnamon is a precious medicine used for treatment, cooking and beauty that is loved today. Cinnamon powder 35g is made from ground cinnamon bark, originating in Vietnam.\r\nCinnamon powder is golden brown in color, has a characteristic cinnamon aroma. In cinnamon powder, there are many vitamins and minerals that are good for the body. In addition, they contain fiber and antioxidants.\r\nCinnamon powder is made from 100% pure cinnamon powder, which is a clean food, ensuring the health of users. They help increase blood circulation, support the treatment of cardiovascular disease, fight cancer, cure flu.\r\nUsing cinnamon powder helps to treat acne, lose weight. Cinnamon powder also helps to stimulate the taste and reduce the fishy smell of dishes.\r\nWith these great uses, cinnamon powder is considered a natural \"panacea\".\r\nCinnamon powder 35g is stored at room temperature in a cool, dry place and away from moisture. After use, it is recommended to close the lid of the jar carefully so as not to lose the scent of cinnamon.', 6, 'img399.png', 100),
(404, 'Organic Galangal Powder Lumlum30g', '4.00', 'Galangal is a rich source of sodium, iron, fiber, vitamins A, C and flavanoids… These nutrients play an important role in maintaining the health of the body. The product is processed into a powder form that makes it easy to use in cooking.\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% organic galangal\r\n\r\nUsage: The product is used as a condiment in curries, baked goods, ... to bring delicious taste, stimulate the palate.\r\n\r\nStorage: Store in a cool place, away from direct sunlight', 6, 'img400.png', 100),
(405, 'Dace Organic Lemongrass Powder 40g', '3.00', 'Made in Viet Nam\r\nCertified organic USDA, EU\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% organic lemongrass.\r\n\r\nPreserved in dry, cool place. Close the cap tightly after each use.', 6, 'img401.png', 100),
(406, 'Organic Lemongrass Powder Lumlum30g', '4.00', 'With a characteristic spicy, warm and aromatic flavor, lemongrass powder is often used in many Thai dishes, helping to eliminate fishy odors and enhance the flavor of dishes. Lemongrass is the main ingredient of the curry spice blend.\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% organic lemongrass\r\n\r\nUses\r\n\r\nLemongrass has the effect of supporting poor digestion, slow digestion, bloating, nausea, vomiting, stimulating bowel movements, stomach pain, clear heat, intestinal spasms, diarrhea. Lemongrass also detoxifies the body by increasing the amount and frequency of urination. This helps keep the liver, digestive tract, pancreas, kidneys, and bladder clean and healthy by assisting the body to eliminate unwanted toxins and uric acid through the urine.\r\n\r\nHow to use\r\n\r\nLemongrass powder is used to cook curries, Thai hot pot, bake cakes or use as a seasoning for grilled dishes, cooking soups, frying, stir-frying, creating a delicious taste.\r\nHelps eliminate fishy odors and add flavor to dishes.\r\nFor people with high blood pressure, eating a lot of lemongrass has the effect of increasing blood circulation, helping to reduce all blood pressure problems. Drinking a glass of lemongrass juice can significantly lower blood pressure. If you suffer from body aches, the essence in lemongrass can relieve all kinds of inflammation, aches and pains. So, if you have toothache, muscle pain, joint pain or pain in other parts, drink lemongrass tea to relieve the pain.', 6, 'img402.png', 100),
(407, 'Vipep Dill Powder 40g', '1.00', 'Dill powder has a characteristic strong and warm flavor due to its high content of essential oils, used as a seasoning to prepare cabbage dishes, ketchup, curries, or casseroles, meat rolls. Used to marinate in many dishes such as poached eggs, grilled meat\r\n\r\n– Ingredients: 100% dill leaves\r\n\r\n- Preserved in dry, cool place.\r\n\r\n– Packing: 35g jar\r\n\r\n- Made in Viet Nam', 6, 'img403.png', 100),
(408, 'Lumlum Organic Black Pepper Powder30g', '5.00', 'Certified organic EU, USDA Specification: 30g jar Ingredients: 100% organic black pepper powder. Preserved in dry, cool place. Close the cap tightly after each use.\r\n\r\nLumlum Organic Black Pepper Powder 30g EU, USDA certified organic\r\nSpecification: 30g . jar\r\nIngredients: 100% organic black pepper powder.\r\nPreserved in dry, cool place. Close the cap tightly after each use.', 6, 'img404.png', 100),
(409, 'Vinasamex Organic Black Pepper Powder 50g', '3.00', 'Ingredients: 100% Vietnamese organic black pepper powder\r\nMade in Viet Nam\r\nInstructions for use: Use as a cooking seasoning\r\nStorage: Store in a cool, dry place, away from direct sunlight\r\nCertified organic EU, USDA, JAS, Korea\r\n\r\nVietnam Cinnamon Export and Production Joint Stock Company (VINASAMEX., JSC) was established in 2012, on the basis of nearly 10 years of experience in the field of manufacturing and trading cinnamon, anise and cinnamon products. spice. VINASAMEX is a pioneering premium star anise brand in Vietnam that builds and manufactures under a closed value chain to produce pure quality products from the Northern mountains and forests, sustainably accompanying highland farmers, representative to raise the level of Vietnamese anise cinnamon products in the international market.\r\n\r\nWith the motto of accompanying upland farmers, VINASAMEX brings long-term cooperation for mutual development, dedicated to taking care of the interests and prosperous life of farmers. From 2017 to now, with an effort to improve knowledge of sustainable agriculture for the highlanders, VINASAMEX continuously expands the production model of cinnamon, anise and organic spices. From 868 hectares of organic cinnamon and anise, associated with 418 households in 2017, so far, VINASAMEX has built 4367 hectares of organic cinnamon, anise and turmeric material areas, associated with 2115 households in Yen provinces. Bai, Lang Son, Lao Cai and Bac Can. People associated with VINASAMEX are able to consume 100% of their output at a price higher than the market price, guaranteed income, peace of mind in production, and improved living standards.', 6, 'img405.png', 100),
(410, 'Dace Organic Garlic Powder 65g', '6.00', 'Food Ingredients:\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% dried garlic powder.\r\n\r\n– Brand: Dace\r\n\r\n-  Made in Viet Nam\r\n\r\n– Weight: 65g\r\n\r\n- Age of use: from 6 months and up\r\n\r\n– Expiry date: 2022\r\n\r\nGeneral introduction:\r\n\r\nDACE Organic Garlic Powder 65g is made from organic garlic grown in the autumn-winter season in the northern region of Vietnam. Garlic plants are planted and grown in the cool autumn weather. When the garlic bulb thrives, the northeast monsoon comes to make the garlic astringent, with a more spicy aroma.', 6, 'img406.png', 100),
(411, 'Lumlum Organic Garlic Powder 50g', '6.00', 'Certification: USDA, EU Organic Farm\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% organic garlic powder\r\n\r\nEffect: Garlic has very good natural antibiotic properties, it helps to keep the digestive system clean by flushing out toxins. Garlic also builds immunity against the common cold and prevents heart disease by clearing clogged arteries. Garlic has the function of stabilizing blood cholesterol, reducing bad cholesterol and increasing good cholesterol. So when you eat garlic regularly, your body will have a stable cholesterol level, reducing the risk of cardiovascular disease\r\n\r\nWith a powder form, garlic easily penetrates food quickly with only a small amount, which is very suitable for marinating baked dishes, making dipping sauces and seasoning foods.\r\n\r\nGarlic powder will be an effective tool, helping to quickly penetrate food, used to marinate food, especially baked dishes, seasoning soups, soups, dipping sauces, etc.', 6, 'img407.png', 100),
(412, 'Vinasamex Organic Garlic Powder 50g', '4.00', 'Ingredients: 100% Vietnamese organic garlic powder\r\nMade in Viet Nam\r\nInstructions for use: Use as a cooking seasoning\r\nStorage: Store in a cool, dry place, away from direct sunlight\r\nCertified organic EU, USDA, JAS, Korea\r\n\r\nVietnam Cinnamon Export and Production Joint Stock Company (VINASAMEX., JSC) was established in 2012, on the basis of nearly 10 years of experience in the field of production and sales of cinnamon, anise and cinnamon products. spice. VINASAMEX is a pioneering premium star anise brand in Vietnam that builds and manufactures under a closed value chain to produce pure quality products from the Northern mountains and forests, sustainably accompanying highland farmers, representative to raise the level of Vietnamese anise cinnamon products in the international market.\r\n\r\nWith the motto of accompanying upland farmers, VINASAMEX brings long-term cooperation for mutual development, dedicated to taking care of the interests and prosperous life of farmers. From 2017 to now, with an effort to improve knowledge of sustainable agriculture for the highlanders, VINASAMEX continuously expands the production model of cinnamon, anise and organic spices. From 868 hectares of organic cinnamon and anise, associated with 418 households in 2017, so far, VINASAMEX has built 4367 hectares of organic cinnamon, anise and turmeric material areas, associated with 2115 households in Yen provinces. Bai, Lang Son, Lao Cai and Bac Can. People associated with VINASAMEX are able to consume 100% of their output at a price higher than the market price, guaranteed income, peace of mind in production, and improved living standards.', 6, 'img408.png', 100),
(413, 'Cocovie Organic Cooking Coconut Oil 450g', '6.00', 'Special Features of Cocovie\'s Cooking Coconut Oil\r\n\r\nRich in Lauric Acid: supports the digestive process, creating a feeling of lightness\r\nHigh smoke point: makes food safe when frying at high temperatures\r\nUnrefined: protect health, reduce cancer risk', 6, 'img409.png', 100),
(414, 'Cocovie Organic Premium Coconut Oil 260ml', '8.00', 'Premium coconut oil - keep your belly beautiful thanks to fat - with 100% organic coconut extract, rich in lauric acid, which converts to energy quickly without accumulating fat like other fats.\r\n\r\nIngredients: Ingredients: 100% organic coconut\r\n\r\nHow to use\r\n\r\nTake 1-2 teaspoons before each meal\r\nUsed to mix vegetables, salads\r\nAdd directly to tea, coffee, milk, juice and other popular drinks, both nutritious and flavor enhancement.', 6, 'img410.png', 100),
(415, 'Bragg Organic Cold Pressed Extra Virgin Olive Oil 473ml', '14.00', 'Extra Virgin Olive Oil Bragg: USDA Organic Certified Organic Premium oil first pressed, acidity 0.51% (world standard =<0.8%) Unrefined, unfiltered Rich in unrefined short-chain fats heart-healthy saturation and antioxidants Meets and exceeds the standards of Olive Oil published by The International Olive Oil Council\'s (IOOC) for quality and purity beautiful over the centuries\r\n\r\nFor fresh produce, the actual weight may vary by about 10%.\r\n\r\nHow to use:\r\n\r\nPerfect for mixing salads, pasta, vegetables, sauces, vinegars, even popcorn. You can also deep fry this Extra Virgin Olive Oil.\r\n\r\nPreserve:\r\n\r\nShould be stored in a cool, dry place, protected from sunlight.\r\n\r\nFor more information about Extra Virgin Olive Oil (EVOO) Bragg:\r\n\r\nExtra Virgin is only the first pressed oil to bring out the best quality with the most nutrients. For Olive oil in general, there will be other types like Virgin/Pure/Pomance, only later pressings make the quality of the oil worse.\r\n\r\n– Cold pressing refers to the method of pressing oil that is not affected by oxidation by temperature.\r\n\r\n– Organic refers to the method of growing olives that are not contaminated by GMOs and chemicals.\r\n\r\n– Color: EVOO will have a darker color than other lines of Olive oil, EVOO Bragg has a very beautiful golden brown color.\r\n\r\nTaste: Taste is also a qualitative factor in determining whether olive oil is good or not. For good oil you can smell the smell of fresh olives.\r\n\r\nThe free acid index is an important indicator to evaluate the quality of olive oil. For the EVOO series according to the international standard of IOOC it is less than 0.8%, but for the EVOO Bragg it is 0.51% lower than the general standard. The reason olive oil is better, the lower this number is because the oil is actually an ester of a fatty acid. In the process of pressing under the effects of oxidizing oil, the bonds will be broken to create free acids. Thus, the free acid reflects the oxidizing effect of the cooking oil. The higher this number, the more oxidized the oil and the stronger the smell.\r\n\r\nBy determining this index will determine the quality of the EVOO, it is also an important parameter for people to be able to determine how fake EVOO oil is. In fact, there are many fake EVOOs on the market today.– The peroxide ratio determines the initial oxidation of an oil. Peroxidation is oxidation. Exposure to heat, light, and metal surfaces accelerates oil oxidation.\r\n\r\nThe lower this value, the longer the oil will retain its shelf life and will delay the possibility of going rancid, while a high peroxide value usually indicates poor handling and low quality of the oil. Thus Olive Oil has a low peroxide value which means it is more stable and if stored properly, the shelf life is extended.\r\nEVOO Bragg has a peroxide index of 10.8 meqO2/kg, while the standard of IOOC is <= 20 meqO2/kg', 6, 'img411.png', 100);
