(429, 'Vipep Thai Hot Pot Seasoning 85g', '2.00', 'Thai hot pot is a favorite dish of many people with its characteristic hot and spicy taste from chili, lemongrass, galangal, and lime leaves. Now you no longer have to spend too much time on preparing ingredients for the broth because you already have the standard Thai Vipep Hot Pot Seasoning 85g.\r\n\r\nHow to cook Thai hot pot with spice packs. First, prepare the ingredients to cook Thai hot pot:\r\nShrimp cut off the legs, head, wash, remove the black thread.\r\nClams are washed through water and then soaked in salt water diluted with a few slices of chili for about 1 hour so that the clams release all the mud and sand.\r\nSquid is washed with water, cut into slices or pieces and then arranged on a plate.\r\nWash the beef and cut it into thin slices.\r\nVegetables and mushrooms remove deep leaves, wilt, then wash and drain.\r\nLemongrass peeled off the outer layer, smashed the white head, cut the body short to put in the decorative hot pot.\r\nTomatoes, fragrant cut into bite-sized pieces.\r\nVipep Thai Hot Pot Seasoning 85g\r\n\r\nSteps to cook hot pot with Thai Vipep Hot Pot Seasoning 85g\r\nPut cooking oil in a pot to boil, then add ½ of the minced garlic and lemongrass and chili. Fry for garlic, lemongrass and chili until fragrant and turn yellow, then continue to add tomatoes and pineapple to stir-fry.\r\nPut 1 - 1.5 liters of water in the pot and then continue to bring the lemongrass that has been cut into pieces along with the lemon leaves to boil. Then add the sliced ​​hot pot package. Add sugar and fish sauce for the broth to taste.\r\nAdd 1 tablespoon of satay chili sauce, chili fruit to the pot of Thai hot pot to increase the aroma and make the hot pot look attractive. Then remove the pot of broth with seafood, dipping vegetables, vermicelli or noodles and a cup of dipping sauce to complete.', 6, 'img425.png', 100),
(430, 'Vipep Pho Seasoning 25g', '1.00', 'Net weight: 25g Packing: Spice pack with full of typical herbs to make pho taste delicious. The product does not contain impurities, synthetic colors and artificial preservatives. The package includes a convenient filter bag.\r\n\r\nPho is a dish that has become a culinary trademark of Vietnam.\r\n\r\nPho is a special gift. Not only in Vietnam, but only in Vietnam, it is delicious, it can be said that one of the indispensable ingredients to help create that special flavor is dried cardamom, cinnamon and star anise. ,\r\n\r\nHowever, these materials are not sold everywhere and are of guaranteed quality. That\'s why Vipep Pho seasoning pack was born and became a great assistant of the sisters behind the success of each bowl of pho.\r\n\r\nThe seasoning package for cooking pho with carefully selected ingredients and a standard ratio of ingredients, you just need to follow the instructions and you will definitely succeed.\r\n\r\nUsage is also very simple:\r\n\r\n1 pack of spices used for 2-3 liters of water\r\nPut the bones in the casserole with 2-3 liters of water\r\nPre-roast the spice pack (roast cardamom, cinnamon, anise first; then roast the rest of the spices), stir until fragrant)\r\nPut the roasted seasoning in the filter bag\r\nPut the seasoning bag in the bone broth\r\nSeason to taste', 6, 'img426.png', 100),
