(465, 'Global Organics Egg-Free Mayonnaise 240g', '9.00', 'Characteristics :\r\n\r\nIt is a specialized product for vegetarians with organic standards.\r\nContains no eggs, milk, soy…\r\nThe taste is extremely delicious, low in fat, so it is not boring to eat.\r\nPackaged in a convenient bottle for use and storage.\r\nCan be used with sandwiches, sauces, dips. Global Organics Eggless Mayonnaise 240G is a sauce made from organic ingredients from Australia. This sauce is egg-free, vegan, but has a rich, delicious flavor. Global Organics Mayonnaise Sauce not only contributes to providing families with delicious meals, but also ensures nutrition and health for the whole family.\r\nProduct Description :\r\n\r\nGlobal Organics Mayonnaise Sauce is a vegan product, suitable for those who are vegetarian or do not like the taste of eggs.\r\nThe product has an extremely delicious taste, low in fat, so it is not boring to eat, helping to increase the taste of food.\r\nThis is a sauce made from organic ingredients from Australia\r\nIn particular, the product is Gluten-free, non-GMO, dairy-free, nut-free, lactose-free, soy-free...\r\nThe sauce is neatly packed in small jars, so in addition to family use, you can also carry it on trips and picnics.', 6, 'img461.png', 100),
(466, 'Organic Eggless Mayonnaise Sottolestelle 230g', '7.00', 'It is a specialized product for vegetarians with organic standards. Does not contain eggs, milk, soy ... The taste is extremely delicious, low in fat, so it is not boring to eat. Packaged in a convenient bottle for use and storage. Can be used with sandwiches, sauces, dips European Certified Organic No Eggs. Completely vegan No Dairy Imported directly from Europe Fresh ingredients, carefully selected. The product does not contain harmful chemicals and preservatives, ensuring safety for consumers\' health.\r\n\r\nThis sauce is egg-free, vegan, but has a rich, delicious flavor. Mayonnaise Sottolestelle not only contributes to providing families with delicious meals, but also ensures nutrition and health for the whole family.\r\n\r\nAs a vegan product, suitable for those who are vegetarian or do not like the taste of eggs.\r\nThe product has an extremely delicious taste, low in fat, so it is not boring to eat, helping to increase the taste of food.\r\nThis is a sauce made from organic ingredients from Italy\r\nIn particular, the product is Gluten-free, non-GMO, dairy-free, nut-free, lactose-free, soy-free.\r\nThe sauce is neatly packed in small jars, so in addition to family use, you can also carry it on trips and picnics.', 6, 'img462.png', 100),
(467, 'Wan Ja Shan Organic Mushroom Sauce 296ml', '6.00', 'The product is USDA certified organic, made in the USA. No preservatives, flavor enhancers, gluten or synthetic flavourings are used. Delicious taste, close to Asian people. It takes no time to prepare the sauce, all the spices are encapsulated in this wonderful dipping sauce.\r\n\r\nIngredients: Gluten-free tamari soy sauce (water, soy*, salt), sugar*, starch*, gum*, shiitake powder*. (*from organic farming)\r\n\r\nInstructions for use: Direct use\r\n\r\nStorage: Store in a cool, dry place, avoid direct sunlight. Store refrigerated after opening.\r\n\r\nTHSD: 4 years from date of manufacture\r\n\r\nNSX & HSD: see on product packaging\r\n\r\nNet weight: 296 ml/bottle\r\n\r\nOrigin: USA', 6, 'img463.png', 100),
(468, 'IL Nutrimento Organic Kale Pesto Sauce 130g', '8.00', 'Pesto sauce is a sauce originating from Genoa in Italy. This sauce has been around since the 16th century. Pesto sauce has a fatty taste of cheese, a characteristic aroma from basil or coriander and finally a slight salty taste of salt.\r\n\r\nBesides the indescribable deliciousness, pesto also has many health benefits. Pesto is rich in Vitamin A, Vitamin C, calcium and iron. The calories come from unsaturated fats, the “healthy fats” that support heart health. The real health benefits come from the fact that Pesto sauce is used in place of other sauces like mayo, creamy pasta sauce and ketchup.\r\n\r\nKale pesto adds vitamins, minerals, antioxidants and elektrolytes, which have various benefits for the entire body. It is a rich source of trace minerals including calcium, iron, magnesium, phosphorus, manganese and copper, as well as fiber, lutein, riboflavin and protein.\r\n\r\nPesto Sauce is also rich in antioxidants, Vitamin E, Vitamin C, Monounsaturated Fats,\r\n\r\nPesto Contains Vitamins and Minerals Your Body Needs Like Calcium, Iron, Potassium, Phosphorus, Selenium, Manganese...\r\n\r\nInstead of eating pesto with carbs like pasta, try it with chicken or tofu. Chicken is a low-fat, high-protein addition to your diet.\r\n\r\nAlternatively, use pesto as a flavorful dip for carrots, cucumbers, tomatoes or broccoli\r\n\r\nIf you\'re going to eat pesto pasta, be sure to buy whole grain pasta\r\n\r\nPesto is high in fat and calories, but also contains many nutritious ingredients.\r\n\r\nRich in vitamins, minerals and monounsaturated fats, pesto provides your body with nutrients to stay healthy and keep your heart healthy.\r\n\r\nThere\'s no reason you can\'t enjoy pesto if you\'re still conscious about your diet.\r\n\r\nElement:\r\n\r\nsunflower oil, kale 29%, cashews, lemon juice, pine nuts 2.9%, garlic 1.5%, potato chips, salt..\r\n\r\nUser Manual:\r\n\r\nBoil noodles and mix with Pesto sauce for a rich, fatty pasta dish.\r\n\r\nPrepare the pesto sauce along with the toasted bread. Dipping bread with Pesto sauce is just wonderful.\r\n\r\nIf you are on a weight loss diet, prepare some salad such as avocado, cherry tomatoes, chicken breast, ... and then add Pesto sauce.', 6, 'img464.png', 100),
(469, 'Caesar Salad Organic Gluten Ozganics 350ml', '8.00', 'Ingredients: filtered water, organic sunflower oil, organic apple cider vinegar, organic spices, fish sauce (herring, salt, sugar), organic raw sugar, sea salt, lemon juice, acacia xathan, lemongrass.\r\nOrigin: Australia.\r\nInstructions for use: eat directly with salad, shake well before use.\r\nStorage: Store in a cool, dry place, away from direct sunlight. Close the lid tightly and keep refrigerated after opening.\r\n\r\nCertified organic Aco', 6, 'img465.png', 100),
