(472, 'Lumlum Organic Black Pepper Sauce 200g', '5.00', 'No MSG, No Additives No Added Preservatives and Artificial Colors Ingredients of All Natural Origin European Organic Certified USDA Organic Certified JAS Vegan Non-GMO Carefully Selected Ingredients Made from organic black pepper. Combining traditional know-how with modern Thai production technology. Natural color, no preservatives, no colorants, absolutely safe to use\r\n\r\nThe black pepper mixed with soy sauce creates the characteristic flavor of this sauce.\r\nIn culinary, organic Sriracha chili sauce is often used as a dipping sauce\r\nThe black pepper sauce that is usually served with steak comes with a choice of rice or spaghetti is excellent.\r\nUse clean raw materials, do not use pesticides. Ensure the health of you and your family.', 6, 'img468.png', 100),
