(474, 'Farmer\'s Organic Black Pepper 55g', '5.00', 'Product information:\r\n\r\n– Brand: Farmers\r\n\r\n- Made in Viet Nam\r\n\r\n– Weight: 55g\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% organic whole grain black pepper\r\n\r\nProduct Features:\r\n\r\nBlack foods contain anthocyanin pigments, which reduce the risk of diabetes, heart disease and cancer.\r\n\r\nBlack pepper also has health-protective effects: preventing colds, coughs, abdominal pain, bloating, indigestion, fighting signs of depression, preventing the growth of tumors in the breast . Piperine substances, Vitamin C, A…\r\n\r\nUser manual:\r\n\r\n- Used as seasoning seasoning for dishes such as stir-fries, soups, sauces...\r\n\r\n- Store in a cool, dry place, away from sunlight\r\n\r\nCertified organic USDA, EU', 6, 'img470.png', 100),
(475, 'Vinasamex Organic Whole Grain Black Pepper 50g', '3.00', 'Ingredients: 100% Vietnamese organic black pepper\r\nMade in Viet Nam\r\nInstructions for use: Use as a cooking seasoning\r\nStorage: Store in a cool, dry place, away from direct sunlight\r\nCertified organic EU, USDA, JAS, Korea\r\n\r\nVietnam Cinnamon Export and Production Joint Stock Company (VINASAMEX., JSC) was established in 2012, on the basis of nearly 10 years of experience in the field of production and sales of cinnamon, anise and cinnamon products. spice. VINASAMEX is a pioneering premium star anise brand in Vietnam that builds and manufactures under a closed value chain to produce pure quality products from the Northern mountains and forests, sustainably accompanying highland farmers, representative to raise the level of Vietnamese anise cinnamon products in the international market.\r\n\r\nWith the motto of accompanying upland farmers, VINASAMEX brings long-term cooperation for mutual development, dedicated to taking care of the interests and prosperous life of farmers. From 2017 to now, with an effort to improve knowledge of sustainable agriculture for the highlanders, VINASAMEX continuously expands the production model of cinnamon, anise and organic spices. From 868 hectares of organic cinnamon and anise, associated with 418 households in 2017, so far, VINASAMEX has built 4367 hectares of organic cinnamon, anise and turmeric material areas, associated with 2115 households in Yen provinces. Bai, Lang Son, Lao Cai and Bac Can. People associated with VINASAMEX are able to consume 100% of their output at a price higher than the market price, guaranteed income, peace of mind in production, and improved living standards.', 6, 'img471.png', 100),
(476, 'Vinasamex Organic Whole Grain Red Pepper 50g', '3.00', 'Ingredients: 100% Vietnamese organic red pepper\r\nMade in Viet Nam\r\nInstructions for use: Use as a cooking seasoning\r\nStorage: Store in a cool, dry place, away from direct sunlight\r\nCertified organic EU, USDA, JAS, Korea\r\n\r\nVietnam Cinnamon Export and Production Joint Stock Company (VINASAMEX., JSC) was established in 2012, on the basis of nearly 10 years of experience in the field of production and sales of cinnamon, anise and cinnamon products. spice. VINASAMEX is a pioneering premium star anise brand in Vietnam that builds and manufactures under a closed value chain to produce pure quality products from the Northern mountains and forests, sustainably accompanying highland farmers, representative to raise the level of Vietnamese anise cinnamon products in the international market.\r\n\r\nWith the motto of accompanying upland farmers, VINASAMEX brings long-term cooperation for mutual development, dedicated to taking care of the interests and prosperous life of farmers. From 2017 to now, with an effort to improve knowledge of sustainable agriculture for the highlanders, VINASAMEX continuously expands the production model of cinnamon, anise and organic spices. From 868 hectares of organic cinnamon and anise, associated with 418 households in 2017, so far, VINASAMEX has built 4367 hectares of organic cinnamon, anise and turmeric material areas, associated with 2115 households in Yen provinces. Bai, Lang Son, Lao Cai and Bac Can. People associated with VINASAMEX are able to consume 100% of their output at a price higher than the market price, guaranteed income, peace of mind in production, and improved living standards.', 6, 'img472.png', 100),
(477, 'Farmer\'s Organic Peppermint 55g', '6.00', 'Made in Viet Nam\r\nCertified organic USDA, EU\r\nIngredients: 100% organic whole-grain black pepper (white pepper)\r\n\r\nPepper is the most commonly used spice in the world. It has been used throughout history in herbal medicine and to preserve foods. White pepper (Piper nigrum) is a flowering plant in the family Piperaceae. You will be surprised that white pepper has so many health benefits:\r\n\r\n1. Anti-cancer.\r\nResearch from Dalhousie University shows that treatment with white pepper can help fight colon cancer.\r\n\r\n2. Aids in digestion.\r\nWhite pepper helps the body secrete more hydrochloric acid, which is necessary for the digestion of proteins and other food components. In addition, white pepper possesses a significant amount of fiber. Fiber stimulates peristaltic movement and increases gastric secretion, making it easier to digest, preventing conditions like constipation, and protecting the body from more serious diseases like colorectal cancer.\r\n\r\n3. Anti-oxidation.\r\nWhite pepper possesses a subtle amount of manganese, which is an essential cofactor in several enzymes important in antioxidant defense.\r\n\r\n4. Improve oral health.\r\nWhite pepper fights tooth decay and provides quick pain relief.\r\n\r\n5. Piperine in white pepper, has been shown to be effective against vitiligo, a skin disease that causes areas of the skin to lose pigmentation.\r\n\r\n6. Helps to lose weight.\r\nResearchers from Sejong University in Seoul, South Korea suggest that the piperine in white pepper fights fat by preventing the formation of new fat cells.\r\n\r\n7. Improves Bone Health\r\nWhite pepper contains minerals, such as manganese, copper and magnesium, which are essential for healthy bone growth and health, especially as people begin to age, and their bones gradually weaken. Go', 6, 'img473.png', 100),
(478, 'Vinasamex Organic Whole Grain Pepper 50g', '4.00', 'Ingredients: 100% Vietnamese organic black pepper\r\nMade in Viet Nam\r\nInstructions for use: Use as a cooking seasoning\r\nStorage: Store in a cool, dry place, away from direct sunlight\r\nCertified organic EU, USDA, JAS, Korea\r\n\r\nVietnam Cinnamon Export and Production Joint Stock Company (VINASAMEX., JSC) was established in 2012, on the basis of nearly 10 years of experience in the field of production and sales of cinnamon, anise and cinnamon products. spice. VINASAMEX is a pioneering premium star anise brand in Vietnam that builds and manufactures under a closed value chain to produce pure quality products from the Northern mountains and forests, sustainably accompanying highland farmers, representative to raise the level of Vietnamese anise cinnamon products in the international market.\r\n\r\nWith the motto of accompanying upland farmers, VINASAMEX brings long-term cooperation for mutual development, dedicated to taking care of the interests and prosperous life of farmers. From 2017 to now, with an effort to improve knowledge of sustainable agriculture for the highlanders, VINASAMEX continuously expands the production model of cinnamon, anise and organic spices. From 868 hectares of organic cinnamon and anise, associated with 418 households in 2017, so far, VINASAMEX has built 4367 hectares of organic cinnamon, anise and turmeric material areas, associated with 2115 households in Yen provinces. Bai, Lang Son, Lao Cai and Bac Can. People associated with VINASAMEX are able to consume 100% of their output at a price higher than the market price, guaranteed income, peace of mind in production, and improved living standards.', 6, 'img474.png', 100),
(479, 'Biovegan Organic Corn Starch 250g', '9.00', 'Ingredients: 100% organic corn starch.\r\n\r\nInstructions for use: 1 teaspoon full is equivalent to 10g starch. 1 full tablespoon is equivalent to 20g of starch.\r\n\r\n+ Use for 500ml liquid: Mix corn starch in a little cold liquid until the powder is completely dissolved, Pour the remaining mixture into the hot liquid and bring to a boil for 1 minute. For example: To make 500ml of soup, you need to dissolve 15-20g of corn starch in 20ml of cold water. Then pour the mixture into the rest of the broth and bring to a boil for 1 minute.\r\n\r\n. Soups: 15g-20g corn starch (for 500ml liquid).\r\n\r\n. Sauces: 20g-25g corn starch (for 500ml liquid).\r\n\r\n. Creamy fruit sauces: 25g - 30g of corn starch (for 500ml of liquid).\r\n\r\n. Flan: 30g – 35g corn starch (for 500ml of liquid).\r\n\r\nUse for pastry recipes: Replace ⅓ of the flour in the recipe with organic cornstarch.\r\n\r\nStorage Instructions: Store in a cool, dry place. Avoid sources of heat and moisture.\r\n\r\nOrigin: Germany\r\n\r\nEU organic certification.', 6, 'img475.png', 100),
(480, 'Wan Ja Shan Organic Sweet Soy Sauce (Hoisin Sauce)230g', '8.00', 'Origin: USA Certified organic USDA\r\n\r\nFor fresh produce, the actual weight may vary by about 10%.\r\n\r\nThis is a special Sauce that is crystallized from healthy ingredients such as soy sauce, soybeans, vinegar, corn starch, and ginger. The taste is sweet and sour, rich and DELICIOUS.\r\n\r\nA special thing is that Hoisin Sauce is used as a condiment for Vietnamese traditional Pho, completely replacing the usual black sauce on the market. In addition, this sauce can also be used in salad rolls, beef balls or marinated spices for many famous Chinese dishes such as char siu, roasted duck.\r\n\r\nSTOP using regular soy sauces with flavor enhancers, preservatives, and synthetic colors. Wan Ja Shan sweet soy sauce meets USDA organic standards, completely safe for long-term use.\r\nBuy 1 bottle can use many dishes such as seasoning for Pho, noodle dishes, beef balls, spring rolls or barbecue seasoning, chicken, char siu, duck\r\nThe product does not contain gluten, the ingredients are completely plant-based, so it is suitable for vegetarians as well.', 6, 'img476.png', 100),
(481, 'Dace Natural Fermented Chili Sauce 250ml', '3.00', 'NATURAL FRESH CHILI SHIP\r\nThe chili sauce is naturally fermented from organic chili and garlic according to the traditional method of Northern Vietnam.\r\n\r\nTo create a delicious and attractive chili sauce, chili is put into incubation no more than 6 hours after harvesting.\r\n\r\nThe natural fermentation process and with 50% chili ingredients plus a little garlic bring out the unique and especially attractive flavor of DACE chili sauce.', 6, 'img477.png', 100),
(482, 'Lumlum Organic Siracha Chili Sauce 250g', '4.00', 'No MSG, No Additives No Added Preservatives and Artificial Colors All-natural Ingredients European Organic Certified USDA Organic Certified JAS Vegan Non-GMO Organic Sriracha Chilli Sauce has Originating from the Sriracha region of Thailand - a country specializing in organic agriculture\r\n\r\nSriracha chili sauce has become one of the most famous chili sauces in the United States and around the world.\r\n\r\nIngredients are carefully selected from organic chili peppers Combining traditional secrets with modern Thai production technology Natural color, no preservatives, no flavorings, absolutely safe to use\r\nThe delicious fresh chili mixed with the strong aroma of garlic creates the typical flavor of Sriracha Organic Chili Sauce Mild spicy combined with sweet, sour and sour spreads to the tip of the tongue, awakening the absolute taste when enjoying the dishes. dish.\r\nIn culinary, organic Sriracha chili sauce is often used as a dipping sauce\r\nSriracha organic chili sauce is very delicious when used with pho, vermicelli, noodles ...\r\nUse as a dip for french fries, fried chicken, pizza, burger…and other fried foods\r\nUse clean raw materials, do not use pesticides. Ensure the health of you and your family.', 6, 'img478.png', 100),
(484, 'Organic Coconut Shredded 250g Sottolestelle 250g', '6.00', 'Origin: Sottolestelle – Italy\r\n\r\nShelf Life : 24 months\r\n\r\nEuropean organic certification\r\n\r\nGluten Free\r\n\r\nNon-GMO\r\n\r\nIngredients: 100% Organic Coconut Shredded\r\n\r\nUses :\r\n\r\nCoconut Sottolestelle is created from the rich, white pulp of a fresh organic coconut and is hand-separated from the shell and cut into small fibers. Slow and careful drying is the last step. No sweeteners, preservatives or whiteners are added.\r\n\r\nCoconut flakes are rich in several important minerals, especially manganese and copper. While manganese supports enzyme function and fat metabolism, copper supports bone formation and heart health\r\n\r\nIn addition, coconut flakes are also rich in fiber, iron, zinc and antioxidants.\r\n\r\nA delicious and versatile ingredient. Coconut flakes are a favorite for housewives who love healthy dishes.\r\n\r\nCan be added to smoothies, cereals, juices, in nut milk recipes. Or topping on baked goods, pancakes', 6, 'img479.png', 100),
